value.description: The identities that needs to be set to the search field on load of the field.

multiple.description: Value 'true' will allow multiple user values to be selected, 'false' will allow only single value selection

scope.description: The scope of search. Valid inputs are 'user', 'group' or 'all'

idbID.description: The identity browser field document element id. It is used to extract the selected identities
